      "palette": {
        "from": "#10151f",
        "via": "#31404f",
        "to": "#c78356"
      },
      "synopsis": "暴雨之夜，你躲进一座破旧古庙。烛火摇曳中，一位白衣女子静坐角落，九尾隐现。",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "暴雨把山路冲成黑河，你推开古庙残门，烛火在狐仙神像前一盏盏颤动。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s00-meet-temple/line-001-550e6326da06.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s00-meet-temple/line-001-550e6326da06.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "550e6326da06",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:38.959Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "右侧的白衣女子静坐在阴影里，身后的九尾银光一闪即逝，像在等你认出她。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s00-meet-temple/line-002-769a994206a4.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s00-meet-temple/line-002-769a994206a4.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "769a994206a4",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:39.936Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "你能上前问清她的来意，也能转身逃向山下，但答案藏在她身后的光里。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s00-meet-temple/line-003-80c8563628ec.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s00-meet-temple/line-003-80c8563628ec.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "80c8563628ec",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:40.804Z"
        }
