    "s01-follow-fox": {
      "id": "s01-follow-fox",
      "chapter": "第一幕",
      "title": "狐仙之路",
      "location": "古庙后院",
      "panorama": "/panoramas/s01-follow-fox.jpg",
      "palette": {
        "from": "#10151f",
        "via": "#31404f",
        "to": "#c78356"
      },
      "synopsis": "你跟随狐仙穿过庭院，她带你走向后山。",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "你跟着她绕过古庙后墙，雨声被庭院里的雾吞没，只剩衣摆擦过石阶的轻响。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-follow-fox/line-001-2f45ad172684.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-follow-fox/line-001-2f45ad172684.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "2f45ad172684",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:41.928Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "她没有回头，却准确说出你梦里反复出现的名字，仿佛这条路你们已经走过很多次。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-follow-fox/line-002-40586ced384f.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-follow-fox/line-002-40586ced384f.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "40586ced384f",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:43.193Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "后山洞口透出灵石微光，你可以继续跟她进去，也可以停下直接逼问她的身份。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-follow-fox/line-003-cd96285e9a6b.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-follow-fox/line-003-cd96285e9a6b.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "cd96285e9a6b",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:44.420Z"
        }
      ],
      "hotspots": [
        {
          "id": "hs01-1",
