    "s01-escape-village": {
      "id": "s01-escape-village",
      "chapter": "第一幕",
      "title": "逃向村庄",
      "location": "山间小路",
      "panorama": "/panoramas/s01-escape-village.jpg",
      "palette": {
        "from": "#10151f",
        "via": "#31404f",
        "to": "#c78356"
      },
      "synopsis": "你拼命跑下山，远处村庄灯火微明。",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "你冲出古庙，山路泥水没过脚踝，身后的烛光像一只不肯闭上的眼。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-escape-village/line-001-a82ed02e2ece.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-escape-village/line-001-a82ed02e2ece.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "a82ed02e2ece",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:45.351Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "村庄的灯火在雨幕里忽明忽暗，远处传来更夫敲梆和低声议论。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-escape-village/line-002-8403fd9967b5.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-escape-village/line-002-8403fd9967b5.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "8403fd9967b5",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:46.175Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "你可以求助村民，把恐惧交给人群，也可以独自查探，弄清那女子为何追进你的梦。",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s01-escape-village/line-003-fbb46dc33d74.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s01-escape-village/line-003-fbb46dc33d74.mp3",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "voiceHash": "fbb46dc33d74",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:47.196Z"
        }
      ],
      "hotspots": [
