    "s02-village-secrets": {
      "id": "s02-village-secrets",
      "chapter": "第二幕",
      "title": "村庄秘闻",
      "location": "村长家",
      "panorama": "/panoramas/s02-village-secrets.jpg",
      "palette": {
        "from": "#10151f",
        "via": "#31404f",
        "to": "#c78356"
      },
      "synopsis": "村长告诉你关于狐仙的可怕传说。",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "村长家的木门紧闭，油灯把老人脸上的皱纹照得像一道道旧伤。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s02-village-secrets/line-001-61b709d99d5d.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s02-village-secrets/line-001-61b709d99d5d.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "61b709d99d5d",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:51.812Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "他说狐仙不是报恩，而是在寻找能替她挡下天劫的人，村里的失踪者都与她有关。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s02-village-secrets/line-002-f9d2e827c194.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s02-village-secrets/line-002-f9d2e827c194.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "f9d2e827c194",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:52.900Z"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "voiceProfileId": "narrator",
          "voiceId": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Radio_Host",
          "voiceStatus": "ready",
          "text": "这些传说可能救你，也可能诱你背叛她；你要查古籍，还是去找她当面求证。",
          "voiceSrc": "/voices/project-20260620-185116/s02-village-secrets/line-003-abee1ec06609.mp3",
          "voiceAssetPath": "assets/voices/s02-village-secrets/line-003-abee1ec06609.mp3",
          "voiceHash": "abee1ec06609",
          "voiceGeneratedAt": "2026-06-20T11:51:53.857Z"
        }
      ],
      "hotspots": [
